snippet.title: C64 Game - Zeppelin
snippet.description:
Levels 5 and 6 of this overlooked gem.

Original Atari 800 game released in 1983 by Synapse Software and programmed by William Mataga. C64 version released in 1984 and converted by David Barbour.

Instructions found here: http://www.atarimania.com/game-atari-400-800-xl-xe-zeppelin_5923.html
